  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/concurrent/atomic/AtomicInteger.html#incrementAndGet()
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/concurrent/ConcurrentMap.html
  [5]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/concurrent/ConcurrentNavigableMap.html
